(1117, 0, '2017-07-09 10:18:20', '2017-07-09 10:18:20', 'GMR is seeking an inside sales professional who loves the challenge of selling into high level executives and is comfortable hunting and closing deals. Challenge yourself and get ready to prove that you have what it takes to be a top producer. This is the best opportunity you can grab as you will be working from home with flexible timings (client  &amp; zone specific).\r\n<h3>Responsibilities</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Responsible for meeting a sales quota in the Municipal, Cooperative, and International Utilities markets.</li>\r\n 	<li>Manage a territory and prospect business on a daily basis via telephone and email.</li>\r\n 	<li>Conducts telephone and web based presentations to close business and increase customer utilization of GMR products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Consistently meet or exceed metrics of 50 calls per day.</li>\r\n 	<li>Conduct occasional face to face sales presentations and attended trade shows to close larger opportunities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Bachelor’s degree in business, marketing or equivalent.</li>\r\n 	<li>3-4 years of face-to-face or inside sales, B2B or Business Development experience.</li>\r\n 	<li>Highly self-motivated and self-disciplined.</li>\r\n 	<li>Outgoing personality with expertise at developing relationships, particularly with operations managers, engineers and technicians.</li>\r\n 	<li>Good communicator—excellent listening skills and ability to undercover the real problems that a client might be experiencing</li>\r\n 	<li>Ability to begin work immediately</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan includes</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New hire and ongoing training and development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Established territory with market leading products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Work from home.</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account.</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves an