(1119, 0, '2017-07-09 10:30:23', '2017-07-09 10:30:23', 'Just as the name suggests, we are currently looking for tech support. Grab on to this as this is one of our work from home opportunities you can find (freshers can apply).\r\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Strong work ethic, detail oriented as well as excellent oral and written communication skills <strong>is mandatory</strong>.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of multiple desktop programs, configuration and debugging techniques.</li>\r\n 	<li>Should have knowledge in windows , installation, troubleshooting, router configuration.</li>\r\n 	<li>Must have good knowledge in Desktop &amp; Networks basic.</li>\r\n 	<li>Knowledge of git and Linux environment is a plus.</li>\r\n 	<li>Sound problem resolution, judgment and decision-making</li>\r\n 	<li>Troubleshooting Windows Installation Technical Support Problem Resolution Router Configuration Communication Skills</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Good to have</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>UG: B.Com - Commerce, B.A - Any Specialization, BCA - Computers, B.Sc - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics, Maths, B.Tech/B.E. - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics/Telecommunication</li>\r\n 	<li>PG: MCA - Computers, MS/M.Sc(Science) - Any Specialization, Computers, Electronics &amp; Embedded Technology, Electronics, M.Com - Commerce.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Benefit Plan includes:</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>New hire and ongoing training and development.</li>\r\n 	<li>Established territory with market leading products.</li>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Health Savings Account.</li>\r\n 	<li>Supplemental Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>Employer paid Life Insurance.</li>\r\n 	<li>30+ Paid leaves annually.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Tech Support', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tech-support', '', '', '2017-07-09 10:30:23', '2017-07-09 10:30:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=1119', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
